Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.72,0:00:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.12,0:00:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同盟军的舰队\N马上就要进入交战空域了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.41,0:00:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}弃子\NResign
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.66,0:01:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌方射程极限12哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.60,0:01:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下降速度过快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.20,0:01:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就保持这个下降速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.37,0:01:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下降到可以用目测进行交战的\N可能距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.90,0:01:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE表面发生变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.30,0:01:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是触手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前发生大量爆炸闪光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.52,0:01:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于视线不佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.65,0:01:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法用目测判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.95,0:01:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE的触手正不分敌我的\N在攻击附近船舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.79,0:01:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左翼戴汀号，庄严号遭击沈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.73,0:01:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在两分钟里我方的战舰\N就被击沈了四分之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.93,0:01:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会变成消耗战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.80,0:01:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争就是消耗战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使流再多的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.24,0:01:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也要趁现在让世界\N从基尔特的统治下获得解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.78,0:01:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要把艾儿薇丝．汉弥尔敦\N和第四个关键谜诗到达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.41,0:02:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就能把EXILE的系统\N自戴芬妮的控制下切离出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为此，即使会失去所有战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.56,0:02:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也必须打倒戴芬妮总帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.16,0:02:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方战舰维持原速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入战斗行列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，又击沈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先锋艇队出动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了，在这种视线下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.52,0:02:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甩开触手杀出一条血路来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.33,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大伙拼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.76,0:03:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反应挺不错的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.19,0:03:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.93,0:03:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥，住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，不可以理他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.23,0:03:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然不理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.91,0:03:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然不理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉，要输掉了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度不能再提高点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.32,0:03:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点钟方向有雨候鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到终点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨候鸟晓得路在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.54,0:04:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉，要输掉了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.94,0:04:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度不能再提高点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.32,0:04:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要顺着风走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉你下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了，成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.08,0:04:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们赢过英麦曼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不对，鲁修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因为我叫你下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因为我叫你下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这世界也走到了尽头是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湖中那扇巨大的门打开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE加快了下降速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌方旗舰还在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.84,0:05:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丝毫不见损伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.55,0:05:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有时间犹豫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.75,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突破战线，直捣戴芬妮总帅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.22,0:06:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会保护您的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改变舰队阵形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有战舰都已并排在本舰两舷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.87,0:06:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着乌尔班号，第三航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标，戴芬妮总帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.71,0:06:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是迪奥也在的话\N一定会更有意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.49,0:06:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我们的皇帝来开路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体战舰，开始炮击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.14,0:06:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE放出的触手的声音\N太多了数不清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有炮门准备发射\N定时信管鱼雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.58,0:07:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备鱼雷，定时信管12秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.42,0:07:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5秒就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要撞到乌尔班号了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开一至三号主炮塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.77,0:07:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标，我方战舰乌尔班号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船员退到船舰前方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.94,0:07:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.97,0:07:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前进方向仰角20度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动力全开，最大航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.89,0:07:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，打倒总帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，这样才漂亮嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被触手包围了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.18,0:08:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体炮门发射喷射破甲弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.29,0:08:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要碰到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.02,0:08:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.86,0:08:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算用拖的也要前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.78,0:08:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不清楚方向了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.96,0:08:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时\N她看着正步向死亡的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉丝...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,渐减口径式重高角炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.56,0:09:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从戴芬妮的船上\N听到了舰长的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞向天空...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.17,0:10:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，两点钟方向有一道光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.84,0:10:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用加速装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.71,0:10:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.37,0:10:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能在这时候发生红视现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.28,0:10:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.91,0:10:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.79,0:11:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大风暴区...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被我们越过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.26,0:11:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是度西斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.52,0:11:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...是度西斯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.89,0:11:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.02,0:11:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.19,0:11:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿，你害怕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.66,0:11:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.87,0:11:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮舰的残骸要撞到地面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体人员准备下船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位的战斗配置可以解除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银之战舰...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.34,0:12:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带我到EXILE那里去，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.78,0:12:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.68,0:12:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副舰长，请下船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.73,0:12:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葳娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.66,0:12:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.79,0:12:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长...他说了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.16,0:12:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他喊了苏菲亚...\N副舰长您的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，葳娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.81,0:13:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乌尔班号...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.39,0:13:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是克劳士机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.87,0:13:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你终于越过了大风暴区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.11,0:13:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了，艾儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.94,0:13:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在天空的彼方存在的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.82,0:13:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指引迷路的孩子\N回到母亲手中的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.46,0:14:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把大地染成金色的波浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抚育生命万物之气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小麦之大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.47,0:14:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使降落的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.97,0:14:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是巨大的风之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大风暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.79,0:14:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在记忆的彼方存在的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切诞生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切回归的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.63,0:15:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.61,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些人还真是不轻言放弃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浮上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浮上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.18,0:17:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今后我永远还是你的副官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖的画啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.66,0:17:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.53,0:17:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，葛温他都哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.73,0:17:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才没哭，这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.07,0:17:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你这大叔没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁是大叔来着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.21,0:17:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽丝，请带我一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看他们俩大概是觉得寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们谁不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.08,0:17:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔又哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.55,0:17:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那这滴滴落的玩意是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是...这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顶级水啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.03,0:17:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在EXILE内部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.10,0:17:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现了爸爸他们的先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.88,0:18:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是爸爸他们的委托筒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.95,0:18:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们俩独处一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.98,0:18:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.76,0:18:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他们努力到了最后一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.61,0:18:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.58,0:18:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.65,0:18:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.30,0:19:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间已没有\N安那托勒和度西斯之分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.37,0:19:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不分基尔特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.31,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他们出发那天所说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.94,0:19:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个没有纷争的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.28,0:19:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今后要靠我们大家一起来打造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是要抓对时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来了，瞌睡虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，吃午饭啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.03,0:20:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃午饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.07,0:20:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.28,0:20:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要飞啰，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.83,0:21:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼回转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该吃午饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.71,0:21:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流动的白云
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.11,0:22:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拂过脸颊的一阵凉风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.78,0:22:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这片蓝天里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论多高，无论多远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.26,0:22:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都可以自由飞翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.07,0:22:25.50,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,无际天空的彼方\N{\c&HFFBF00&}果てない空の彼方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.57,0:22:31.44,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,这一切将连向何方\N{\c&HFFBF00&}すべては何処へ続くだろう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.51,0:22:37.31,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,追寻一处平静的地方\N{\c&HFFBF00&}求める安らぎの場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.38,0:22:43.15,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,天使降落的路\N{\c&HFFBF00&}天使が降りる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.22,0:22:52.06,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信就连在我的手上\N{\c&HFFBF00&}腕へ　きっと続くよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.13,0:22:57.66,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飞往天际\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.74,0:23:03.44,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿成为你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.51,0:23:09.35,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,无论风有多么强\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.42,0:23:15.12,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永远不会折断的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.19,0:23:24.62,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我会拥有那样一对翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
